    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When you say 'neatly styled' and 'conservative,' can you get a bit more specific? For example, what kind of hairstyles or grooming habits would you recommend for different people to ensure they don't look too 'casual' or 'distracting' in a serious boardroom environment?",
