      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. To be practical, I have a client who has very thick, textured hair and prefers to keep it in its natural state rather than straightening it every day. Does that fit into what you're describing as 'well-controlled' and 'polished,' or does that kind of natural texture tend to be seen as too casual for these high-level meetings?",
